    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home. This car is practically flawless\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's been kept spotless inside and out. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. You've gotta see it in person to believe how clean it is!",
