      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle in truly pristine condition. Every inch of the original factory paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirls, chips, or road imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and shows zero signs of wear, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, the car is faultless, backed by a comprehensive, fully documented service history and consistently stored in a climate-controlled garage. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this vehicle has been meticulously preserved for the most discerning buyer. It performs exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line\u2014tight, responsive, and exceptionally smooth.",
