      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty! It\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014no scratches, no spills, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m really sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Everything is pristine and ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin!",
